These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, whist
City: berlin, nizza, marseilles
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, techno, indie
1. the person playing backgammon is between the person traveling to berlin and the fan of soul##2
2. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
3. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Game          | bridge      | backgammon        | whist     |
| City         | marseilles | nizza | berlin    |
| Transport   | roller   | car       | scooter |
| Music-Genre         | soul  | techno      | indie    |

