.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, aconite, orchid
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, grey, pink
There are 3 different nationalities: american, russian, french
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, rock, punk
1. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person who likes grey is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the american##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the russian##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
6. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
7. the fan of punk is between the person who likes grey and the person who growslily##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Flower           | aconite    | orchid | lily |
| Color   | grey | lavender       | pink   |
| Nationality           | french  | russian   | american     |
| Music-Genre         | rock | punk       | dubstep   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, aquamarine, blood-red
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, r&b, metal
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, january, december
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, fanta
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
4. the person who likes apricot is between the fan of r&b and the person drinking fanta##2
5. the fan of indie is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Color          | blood-red | apricot | aquamarine |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | indie | r&b |
| Birthday           | january       | march   | december    |
| Beverage     | fanta      | juice   | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, pepper, banana
3 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, mah-jongg
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, rock, disco
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, june, september
1. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the person eating banana##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is the fan of rock##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person eating banana is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Food         | pepper  | lettuce       | banana |
| Game           | mah-jongg     | monopoly      | scrabble   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | metal | disco     |
| Birthday   | july      | september   | june     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, ritmeester, baccarat
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, lily
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, aquamarine, orange
3 different games are played: domino, snooker, poker
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
6. the person who growslily is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
7. the person playing poker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Cigar      | baccarat     | ritmeester   | fonseca         |
| Flower           | azalea | aconite | lily |
| Color   | orange      | aquamarine   | blood-red            |
| Game   | snooker   | poker  | domino         |

