.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter, ship
House: palace, craftsman, colonial
City: nizza, liverpool, boston
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, august
1. the person traveling to liverpool is between the craftsman house and the person driving the scooter##2
2. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person traveling to boston is the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Transport          | ship    | skateboard     | scooter |
| House           | craftsman | colonial | palace      |
| City   | boston      | liverpool       | nizza    |
| Birthday   | november      | february         | august     |

