.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
House: gothic-revival, wooden, ranch-style
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, baking, reading
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, italian, nigerian
3 different games are played: canasta, go, whist
1. the gothic-revival house is in the middle##1
2. the italian is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is the person playing go##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the chinese is between the person playing go and the wooden house##2
7. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| House          | wooden | gothic-revival | ranch-style |
| Hobby   | baking  | skydiving    | reading |
| Nationality   | italian  | chinese   | nigerian    |
| Game     | whist   | canasta       | go |

