.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
House: colonial, victorian, modern
City: san-francisco, colone, paris
3 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, hedgehog
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, sunflower
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
2. the modern house is on the far right##1
3. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the owner of the lizard and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| House      | victorian | colonial    | modern  |
| City         | paris        | san-francisco   | colone   |
| Pet   | hedgehog       | goat    | lizard |
| Flower     | sunflower          | poppy | rose       |

