3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
6. the person who likes black is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday          | september  | february   | november      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta      | juice      |
| Sport   | soccer | tennis | weightlifting    |
| Color           | coral   | black     | mauve |

