.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-11::.
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, bridge
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, march, november
City: rome, edinburgh, berlin
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daisy, bellflower
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Game      | bridge     | backgammon      | canasta  |
| Birthday          | march     | november | october       |
| City   | rome  | berlin    | edinburgh      |
| Flower         | bellflower | zinnia  | daisy |

