.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, trike, bike
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, turquise, blue
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, pop, indie
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, pall-mall, ritmeester
1. the ritmeester-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
5. the fan of pop is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
6. the person who likes white is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
7. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the bus and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Transport      | bike       | trike   | bus |
| Color   | white | blue     | turquise |
| Music-Genre           | d&b      | pop | indie    |
| Cigar         | pall-mall  | ritmeester     | chaman |

