The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, video-games, woodworking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, action, drama
City: marseilles, hamburg, rome
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is the person traveling to rome##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
8. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar           | dannemann | ritmeester   | montecristo |
| Hobby   | fishing  | video-games    | woodworking    |
| Movie-Genre         | action    | time-travel | drama   |
| City     | hamburg  | rome     | marseilles  |

