3. the person who likes emerald is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes light-blue is between the person eating potato and the person who's birthday is in february##2
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Birthday         | december    | march   | february      |
| Food           | potato | zucchini    | grapefruit |
| Transport   | quad-bike       | van | tram      |
| Color         | azure         | light-blue   | emerald     |

