There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, sprite
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish, chinchilla
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes pink is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Game          | domino     | backgammon   | whist     |
| Color   | apricot   | emerald   | pink      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice | sprite    |
| Pet     | chinchilla  | rabbit   | fish |

