3. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
5. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage          | soy-milk     | coffee | iced-tea   |
| Game         | bridge   | go | snooker |
| Color   | apricot | black       | red   |
| Birthday     | may     | june  | july        |

