4. the person playing chess is on the right of the modern house##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
